              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>Cala Falcó Collection is a natural holistic wellness house and aromachologist. The Collection is nourished by botanicals sourced from the wild botanical farm and family home at ‘Cala Falcó’, a coastal sanctuary in Mallorca. The Collection is specifically blended to harness the transformative and potent power of botanicals to awaken your senses and lift your mood.<br/>We are equal parts natural scent scientists, botanists, bespoke lab ateliers, sensory alchemists and artists<br/>We fiercely believe in a connection to nature and a 100% natural and slower approach to sourcing our ingredients.</p>",
